  "content": "<style>\n/* ===== HERO ===== */\n.pk-hero-section {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d5cd9 0%, #2a49c7 100%) !important;\n  color: white !important;\n  padding: 60px 40px;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 34px;\n  width: 100vw !important;\n  margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%) !important;\n  margin-right: calc(-50vw + 50%) !important;\n}\n.pk-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }\n.pk-hero-badge {\n  display: inline-block;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);\n  color: white;\n  padding: 8px 16px;\n  border-radius: 50px;\n  font-size: 0.85rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\n}\n.pk-hero-title {\n  font-size: 3rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n}\n.pk-hero-subtitle {\n  font-size: 1.15rem;\n  opacity: 0.95;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  max-width: 800px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n/* ===== HUB WIDGET ===== */\n:root { --pk-hub-max: 1040px; }\n#pk-blog-hub {\n  max-width: var(--pk-hub-max);\n  margin: 0 auto 72px auto; \n  padding: 0 20px;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n#pk-blog-hub .pk-posthero-lead {\n  text-align: center;\n  max-width: 760px;\n  margin: 0 auto 26px auto;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  opacity: .85;\n}\n#pk-blog-hub .pk-start-title {\n  margin: 0 0 12px 0;\n  font-size: .95rem;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  letter-spacing: .04em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  opacity: .85;\n}\n#pk-blog-hub .pk-start-items {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));\n  gap: 18px 28px;\n  align-items: stretch;\n}\n/* ===== NOVÝ SYSTÉM KARET (Už to není odkaz, ale DIV!) ===== */\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-start-item {\n  display: flex !important;\n  flex-direction: column !important;\n  justify-content: flex-start !important;\n  /* RELATIVE je kritické pro natažení odkazu přes kartu */\n  position: relative !important; \n  padding: 16px 14px !important;\n  box-sizing: border-box !important;\n  min-height: 165px !important; \n  border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px !important;\n  background-color: transparent !important;\n  color: inherit !important;\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12) !important;\n  border-bottom: 0px solid transparent !important;\n  border-left: 0px solid transparent !important;\n  border-right: 0px solid transparent !important;\n  /* Přechod aplikovaný na DIV, nikoliv na odkaz */\n  transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border-top-color 0.2s ease !important;\n}\n/* Hover na DIV - Elementor do divů nešťourá */\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-start-item:hover {\n  border-top-color: #3d5cd9 !important;\n  background-color: rgba(61, 92, 217, 0.04) !important;\n}\n/* ===== STRETCHED LINK (Kouzlo) ===== */\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-stretched-link {\n  color: inherit !important;\n  text-decoration: none !important;\n  box-shadow: none !important;\n  background: none !important;\n}\n/* Toto roztáhne odkaz přes celou plochu karty */\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-stretched-link::after {\n  content: \"\" !important;\n  position: absolute !important;\n  top: 0 !important;\n  right: 0 !important;\n  bottom: 0 !important;\n  left: 0 !important;\n  z-index: 10 !important;\n}\n/* Zrušení všech šablonových nesmyslů na našem nataženém odkazu */\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-stretched-link:hover,\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-stretched-link:focus,\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-stretched-link:active {\n  transform: none !important;\n  text-decoration: none !important;\n  box-shadow: none !important;\n  outline: none !important;\n}\n/* Barva nadpisu při najetí myší kamkoliv na kartu */\nhtml body #pk-blog-hub .pk-start-item:hover .pk-stretched-link {\n  color: #2a49c7 !important;\n}\n/* ===== TYPOGRAFIE ===== */\n#pk-blog-hub span.pk-start-kicker {\n  display: block !important;\n  font-size: .85rem !important;\n  font-weight: 800 !important;\n  opacity: .6 !important;\n  margin-bottom: 6px !important;\n  color: inherit !important;\n}\n#pk-blog-hub h3.pk-start-head {\n  display: block !important;\n  font-size: 1.05rem !important;\n  font-weight: 700 !important;\n  line-height: 1.3 !important;\n  margin: 2px 0 8px 0 !important;\n  padding: 0 !important;\n  min-height: 2.6em !important; \n  background-color: transparent !important;\n}\n#pk-blog-hub span.pk-start-desc {\n  display: block !important;\n  font-size: .96rem !important;\n  line-height: 1.55 !important;\n  opacity: .78 !important;\n  color: inherit !important;\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 1; /* Aby se dal text normálně označit pod odkazem */\n}\n/* ===== MOBIL ===== */\n@media (max-width: 900px) {\n  #pk-blog-hub .pk-start-items { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; }\n  #pk-blog-hub { margin-bottom: 52px; }\n  #pk-blog-hub .pk-start-item { padding-left: 0 !important; padding-right: 0 !important; }\n  html body #pk-blog-hub .pk-start-item:hover { background-color: transparent !important; }\n}\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .pk-hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }\n  .pk-hero-subtitle { font-size: 1rem; }\n  .pk-hero-section { padding: 40px 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; }\n}\n</style>\n<section>\n    BLOG\n    <h1>Blog o AI (umělé inteligenci)</h1>\n    <p>\n      Zkušenosti z praxe, školení a testování nástrojů: ChatGPT, Gemini, Copilot, Perplexity a další. Workflow, bezpečnost i dopady AI na každodenní práci.\n    </p>\n</section>\n  <p>\n    Tenhle blog o AI je rozcestník mých článků, tipů a zkušeností.\n  </p>\n  Začněte tady\n      01\n      <h3>\n        <a href=\"https://pavelkovarik.cz/nejlepsi-ai-asistent-2026-srovnani-chatgpt-gemini-claude-a-dalsich/\">Nejlepší AI asistent v roce 2026</a>\n      </h3>\n      Srovnání ChatGPT, Gemini a Claude. Vyberte si model podle toho, co reálně potřebujete vyřešit.\n      02\n      <h3>\n        <a href=\"https://pavelkovarik.cz/zavedeni-ai-2026/\">Jak zavést AI do praxe v roce 2026</a>\n      </h3>\n      Konec experimentování. Praktický návod, jak zavést AI do firmy tak, aby měla měřitelný dopad a jasnou návratnost.\n      03\n      <h3>\n        <a href=\"https://pavelkovarik.cz/ai-nastroje/\">Seznam AI nástrojů</a>\n      </h3>\n      Aplikace, které sám používám a testuji. Jen to, co dává smysl, průběžně aktualizováno.\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n/* CTA PATIČKA - FINÁLNÍ VERZE */\n.pk-cta-wrapper {\n    max-width: 1000px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 0 24px;\n}\n.pk-cta-section {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d5cd9 0%, #2a49c7 100%) !important;\n    color: #fff !important;\n    padding: 60px 24px;\n    text-align: center;\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    margin: 50px 0;\n}\n.pk-cta-content {\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 2;\n}\n.pk-cta-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);\n    padding: 6px 16px;\n    border-radius: 50px;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\n    color: #fff;\n}\n.pk-cta-title {\n    font-size: 1.8rem !important;\n    font-weight: 800 !important;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem !important;\n    line-height: 1.25 !important;\n    color: #fff !important;\n    font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n}\n.pk-cta-subtitle {\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n    opacity: 0.9;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    max-width: 680px;\n    margin-left: auto;\n    margin-right: auto;\n    color: #fff !important;\n}\n.pk-cta-buttons {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    margin: 1.5rem 0;\n}\n/* Tlačítka podle design systemu */\n.pk-cta-section .pk-btn {\n    display: inline-flex !important;\n    align-items: center !important;\n    justify-content: center !important;\n    min-width: 200px !important;\n    height: 52px !important;\n    padding: 0 32px !important;\n    border-radius: 12px !important;\n    font-weight: 700 !important;\n    text-decoration: none !important;\n    font-size: 1rem !important;\n    border: 2px solid transparent !important;\n    cursor: pointer !important;\n    white-space: nowrap !important;\n    flex-shrink: 0 !important;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease !important;\n    font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n}\n.pk-cta-section .pk-btn-white {\n    background: #fff !important;\n    color: #3d5cd9 !important;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n}\n.pk-cta-section .pk-btn-white:hover {\n    background: #f1f5f9 !important;\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n}\n.pk-cta-section .pk-btn-outline {\n    border-color: #fff !important;\n    color: #fff !important;\n    background: transparent !important;\n}\n.pk-cta-section .pk-btn-outline:hover {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important;\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n}\n.pk-cta-contact {\n    margin-top: 25px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    color: #fff;\n}\n.pk-cta-note {\n    margin-top: 15px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    opacity: 0.9;\n    color: #fff;\n}\n/* Responzivní design */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .pk-cta-wrapper {\n        padding: 0 15px;\n    }\n    .pk-cta-section {\n        padding: 50px 20px;\n        margin: 40px 0;\n    }\n    .pk-cta-title {\n        font-size: 1.5rem !important;\n    }\n    .pk-cta-subtitle {\n        font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n    .pk-cta-buttons {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n    .pk-cta-section .pk-btn {\n        width: 100% !important;\n        max-width: 280px !important;\n    }\n}\n</style>\n    <section>\n            CHCETE TO VYZKOUŠET?\n            <h2>Ukážu vašemu týmu, jak AI skutečně funguje v praxi</h2>\n            <p>\n                Praktické školení AI pro firmy. Bez zbytečné teorie, jen nástroje \n                které váš tým začne používat hned druhý den.\n            </p>\n                <a href=\"/kontakt/\">Nezávazná konzultace</a>\n                <a href=\"tel:+420770126519\">Zavolat: +420 770 126 519</a>\n                📞 +420 770 126 519 · ✉️ mail@pavelkovarik.cz\n            <p>\n                Odpovím do 24 hodin • Škol